Sentencas: Porous Ni-Al-CGO cermet (CGO = Ce0.9Gd0.1O2) for use in solid oxide fuel cells was fabricated by thermal explosion (volume reaction) in Ni-Al-CGO powder compacts in different heat sink conditions.
Titulo: Porous Ni-Al-CGO Cermet for Use in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Temperature profiles of thermal explosion were recorded and analyzed as a function of green composition.
Titulo: Porous Ni-Al-CGO Cermet for Use in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Phase composition of resultant porous materials was found to depend on the CGO content of green mixture and temperature of vacuum annealing.
Titulo: Porous Ni-Al-CGO Cermet for Use in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Starting and final materials were characterized by XRD, SEM, and EDS.
Titulo: Porous Ni-Al-CGO Cermet for Use in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Synthesized uniform cermets with a porosity of 50-60% can be recommended for use as a support for solid oxide fuel cells with Ni/CGO anode.
Titulo: Porous Ni-Al-CGO Cermet for Use in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
